              <span id="reviewTextContainer2073526577" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12802857620281499468">Innocuous enough book: one of those &quot;prodigal child returns to ailing town and everyone&apos;s fortunes improve&quot; stories. Wooden characters, predictable plot, shallow sense of human nature. Would be a great book to leave in a beach house for reading a few pages before bed. </span>
  <span id="freeText12802857620281499468" style="display:none">Innocuous enough book: one of those "prodigal child returns to ailing town and everyone's fortunes improve" stories. Wooden characters, predictable plot, shallow sense of human nature. Would be a great book to leave in a beach house for reading a few pages before bed. </span>
